data.description: This Beautiful 4 bed 3.5 bath Former Highland Model boasts plantation shutters, stone fireplace, ceramic tile in wet areas. Recent 2016 updates include new hardwoods, carpet, designer paint in main areas, water heaters and AC.  The delightful cooks kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless appliances, gas range-oven, walk in pantry, huge island that seats 4 and breakfast area. Master suite has jetted tub, dual sinks and walk in closet. 3 upstairs bedrooms have walk in closets and one has full bath. The pool table and shuffle board game in the game room can be yours if you like. Enjoy movie nights at home in your home theater! HD projector system and screen with surround sound stay with home.
